Megatron noticed Skullgrin was begining to float off by himself. He
scanned the battlefield, upset that his aim had not been true, and now
saw Triggerhappy in danger. He smothely floated in front of SKullgrin,
facing the assault warrior. "Return to base Skullgrin, but be careful."
He then turned and began to soar towards the battlefield again, keeping
his optics straight on Triggerhappy. "Firestrike, are you all right?" He
asked the perplexing Decepticon.
